data.description: This Village of Carthage home is stunning from the inside out! Walk onto the gorgeous hardwood floors through out the home. Great flow in this layout. Large, bright kitchen with nice cabinet space. Generous size island. Spacious eat-in dining room within the kitchen or enjoy your formal dining room.  Great living room size that holds oversized furniture. 1 bedroom on the 1st. floor, 3 bedrooms upstairs. Great full size bathrooms on each floor making it very convenient. The bedrooms are each a great size. Master bedroom has an access door to the upstairs bathroom for private use. Several porches including 1 enclosed porch. New metal roof. Newer hot water heater. Freshly painted throughout. Nice yard space. Close to Fort Drum and shopping amenities. Make an appt. and see all the updates.
